title: HaMitbachon
typeOfFood: Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Israeli, Eastern European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Near the busy Carmel Market in the Kerem HaTaymanim neighborhood, this place offers items on its menu marked with a V. These can be either vegetarian or vegan so ask to be sure. Offers Middle Eastern salads like green techina and roasted eggplant. Mains include stuffed vegetables and majadara, a rice and lentil dish.
